Ring UI: development environment setup

1. Install node.js

2: Install grunt-cli:

    npm install grunt -g

3. Install dependencies:

    npm install && grunt install

4. Build files:

    grunt

5. Start the watcher:

    grunt watch

6. Start the server:

    grunt connect

=======================================

Lint code with jshint:

    grunt jshint

Setup pre-commit jshint hook:

    grunt hooks

Clean generated files:

    grunt cleanup

Uninstall dependencies:

    grunt uninstall
